<p><b>Saks, Inc.</b>, originally <b>Proffitt's Inc.</b> until 1998, is a <a href="/wiki/Fortune_1000" title="Fortune 1000">Fortune 1000</a> operator of high-end department stores in the United States under the nameplate <a href="/wiki/Saks_Fifth_Avenue" title="Saks Fifth Avenue">Saks Fifth Avenue</a>. It was founded in <a href="/wiki/Birmingham,_Alabama" title="Birmingham, Alabama">Birmingham</a>, <a href="/wiki/Alabama" title="Alabama">Alabama</a> and is currently headquartered in <a href="/wiki/New_York_City" title="New York City">New York City</a>.</p>
<p></p>
